{"tid":2120882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"保皇黨眼中釘的羅冠聰，依家保皇黨會有咩感受？","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T11:55:49.000Z","uid":127575,"like":312,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"22dad13c71f24b20a31b6571bd056fb87989b684","tid":2120882,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"羅冠聰去見英國+美國+澳洲官員..........<br />\n<br />\n英國就彭定康<br />\n美國就國務卿蓬佩奧<br />\n澳洲就最高外交使節會面共晉晚餐<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨+西門梓+周浩頂+李家超 表示 ：<br />\n好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 西門梓去狗屋報串羅冠聰違反國安法<br />\n結果話自己求助無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 周浩頂串串眾志 串羅冠聰流亡<br />\n結果眾志解散後+羅冠聰國際線越玩越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 李家超一世都未試過同外國高級官員見面<br />\n心裏應該好葡萄又要好嬲好嬲<br />\n之前仲要想拉黃台仰，結果得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 姐姐就唔洗講🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇<br />\n<br />\n5. 基本上保皇黨想搞冧國際線.....根本搞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰做到保皇黨／港共政府官員做唔到嘅野<br />\n佢地心裏應該唔只好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad92fd6dd2772739a07a6c90000ed65cdf35726e","tid":2120882,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c536e52e991efd9f41e48a239